NORDIC chipsets related repository

nrf24l01p and nrf905 are currently supported. There is an implem for
nrf2401a, not tested.

This repo contains:
. microcontroller code to use the NRF chipsets (refer to src directory),
. host library to communicate with the chipset from LINUX over serial
(refer to snrf/src directory),
. schematics for a serial bridge board (refer to snrf/hw directory).
